    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. Honestly, it's like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged, never a scratch, and the interior still has that new-car smell! It drives like an absolute dream and has been meticulously maintained. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
