    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S represents the pinnacle of analog feedback and mechanical refinement. Powered by a 3.6L flat-six engine, it features a reinforced IMS bearing and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The wide-body chassis retains factory-correct structural integrity, complemented by an upgraded Bilstein coilover system for superior damping and reduced body roll. With its viscous-coupling AWD system and factory sport exhaust, the power delivery is linear and the acoustic profile is unmistakable. Meticulously maintained with zero bore scoring and a documented service history, this example offers a concours-level presentation for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
